FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774185071
OL,3,CDad who lost son to Meningitis B calls
OL,4,Cfor all teenagers to be vaccinated
OL,6,FSome 23 cases have been confirmed in
OL,7,FKent alongside a further 11 cases that
OL,8,F"remain under investigation", the UK
OL,9,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) said in
OL,10,Fan update on Saturday morning. (21
OL,11,FMarch)
OL,13,FEighteen of the 23 confirmed cases are
OL,14,Fmeningitis B, and all cases have
OL,15,Frequired hospital admission.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774185071
OL,3,CDad who lost son to Meningitis B calls
OL,4,Cfor all teenagers to be vaccinated
OL,6,FThe latest figures come as more than
OL,7,F500 people, students and others
OL,8,Feligible, lined up outside the
OL,9,FUniversity of Kent campus clinic for
OL,10,Fmeningitis B jabs at the start of the
OL,11,Fweekend.
OL,13,FMr Berryman said he's devastated for
OL,14,Fthe families of the young people who
OL,15,Fhave died.
OL,17,F"My heart goes out to them," he said.
OL,19,F"I just pray that they make a recovery
OL,20,Fquickly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774185071
OL,3,CDad who lost son to Meningitis B calls
OL,4,Cfor all teenagers to be vaccinated
OL,6,F"But the most brutal thing about it is
OL,7,Fthat this is probably preventable
OL,8,Fbecause we know that the two most
OL,9,Fvulnerable ages are young babies and
OL,10,Fteenagers, especially when they go to
OL,11,Funiversity, a melting pot of bugs and
OL,12,Fthings.
OL,14,F"I would really appeal to Wes
OL,15,FStreeting and the government to get
OL,16,Fthis vaccine in the program for all
OL,17,Fteenagers.
OL,19,F"We know it's going to help."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774185071
OL,3,CDad who lost son to Meningitis B calls
OL,4,Cfor all teenagers to be vaccinated
OL,6,FOn Thursday the Health Secretary
OL,7,Fexpanded his appeal to more people to
OL,8,Fget antibiotics or the vaccine for
OL,9,Fmeningitis.
OL,11,FDr Ben Rush, Consultant in
OL,12,FCommunicable Disease Control at UKHSA
OL,13,Fsaid: "We continue to remain vigilant
OL,14,Ffor new cases and work closely with
OL,15,FNHS England and local authorities
OL,16,Facross the country to ensure enhanced
OL,17,Fsurveillance is in place.
OL,19,F"Any new cases will be identified
OL,20,Fquickly and responded to.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774185071
OL,3,CDad who lost son to Meningitis B calls
OL,4,Cfor all teenagers to be vaccinated
OL,6,F"It's reassuring to have seen so many
OL,7,Feligible young people come forward for
OL,8,Fantibiotics and vaccination and we'd
OL,9,Flike to thank everyone involved in
OL,10,Fthis effort so far.
OL,12,F"It's vital that people are aware of
OL,13,Fthe signs and symptoms of invasive
OL,14,Fmeningococcal disease and seek
OL,15,Fimmediate medical attention if they or
OL,16,Fanyone they know develops symptoms.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
